tooltip_properties.description: Draw a rope logic link between two Rope Nodes to form a cable. Can be extended and retracted.
tooltip_properties.short_description: A mechanical winch that can transfer data/electric/fluid through an attached cable, with an extension length of 600m.

logic_node.label: Down
logic_node.description: Lowers the winch cable down when receiving an on signal.

logic_node.label: Up
logic_node.description: Raises the winch cable up when receiving an on signal.

logic_node.label: Composite Input
logic_node.description: Composite data to send to the connected anchor.

logic_node.label: Composite Output
logic_node.description: Composite data to receive from the connected anchor.

logic_node.label: On/Off Input
logic_node.description: On/Off data to send to the connected anchor.

logic_node.label: On/Off Output
logic_node.description: On/Off data to receive from the connected anchor.

logic_node.label: Video Data Send
logic_node.description: Video data to send to the connected anchor.

logic_node.label: Video Data Receive
logic_node.description: Video data to receive from the connected anchor.

logic_node.label: Audio Data Send
logic_node.description: Audio data to send to the connected anchor.

logic_node.label: Audio Data Receive
logic_node.description: Audio data to receive from the connected anchor.

logic_node.label: Length
logic_node.description: The current length of the winch cable in metres.

logic_node.label: Fluid
logic_node.description: Fluid connection for the hose coil.

logic_node.label: Speed
logic_node.description: The speed of the winch clamped to a relative range of -1 to 1.
